description: REPORT AND RECOMMENDATION Having reviewed the medical evidence of record, the transcript of the administrative hearing, the decision of the administrative law judge, and the pleadings and briefs of the parties, the undersigned Magistrate Judge finds  that the administrative law judge failed to apply correct legal standards as discussed above. Accordingly, it is recommended that the final decision of the Commissioner of Social Security Administration be reversed and that the matter be remanded for  further proceedings consistent with this Report and Recommendation. This Report and Recommendation disposes of all issues referred to the undersigned Magistrate Judge in the captioned matter.re  1  Complaint Social Security filed by Heather Barthel Objections to R&R due by 8/4/2009.
